{"article_id":"GjJyltbRkeCAgT2h","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"At least 13 people have now died in fast-spreading fires","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that are ravaging parts of California 's wine region .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"A state of emergency was declared in northern areas","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"after mass evacuations ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"with 2,000 structures destroyed .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"About 20,000 people fled from Napa , Sonoma and Yuba counties in response to some the state 's worst-ever wildfires .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Such fires are more common in southern California","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"but a combination of dry weather and strong winds has fuelled the destruction in the north .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Cal Fire officials said on Tuesday morning","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that 17 wildfires in nine counties have burned more than 115,000 acres in just the past 12 hours .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"`` These fires have destroyed structures","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and continue to threaten thousands of homes ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"necessitating the evacuation of thousands of residents , ''","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Governor Jerry Brown said .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"President Donald Trump has approved a disaster declaration for the fire-ravaged state ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"allowing federal emergency aid to be sent .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"There is little sign the weather in the coming days will bring much relief to firefighters ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"BBC Weather says .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"More tinder dry conditions are forecast ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"with no rain expected .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Meanwhile , in southern California , a separate wildfire burnt 24 homes or other buildings in the wealthy Anaheim Hills area of Orange County ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"forcing thousands of residents to evacuate .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"What do we know of the loss of life and damage ?","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"The fires","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"- considered among the deadliest in state history -","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"have sent smoke as far south as San Francisco ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"located about 60 miles","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"( 96km )","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"away .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"A new fire is reportedly burning near the Oakmont area of Santa Rosa , a city","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that has already been devastated by the blazes .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Hundreds of homes have been destroyed in the city by flames so hot","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that glass melted on cars .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Details of how the seven people died in Sonoma","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"were not immediately available ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"but country sheriff Rob Giordano said","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"he expected the death toll to rise .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"`` There is a lot of burned homes and a lot of burned areas ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"so it 's just logical that we 're gon na find more people , ''","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Two people also died in Napa county and one in Mendocino county","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"when thousands of acres burned in one valley .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Sonoma County officials said","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"they had received more than 150 missing-person reports by Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Authorities said","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"they have found a few of the missing persons","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"but most of the reports were still under investigation ,","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"Sonoma County spokesman Scott Alonso said .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Dozens of vineyard workers were reportedly airlifted to safety overnight .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Wineries","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"belonging to the rich and famous","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"were abandoned .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"One","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"belonging to musician Dave Matthews","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"was closed and at risk","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"of being burned to the ground ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"staff said ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"as was the nearby Francis Ford Coppola Winery .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"The vine harvest is already under way","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"and many of the grapes have been picked .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"It is not yet known how the fires started on Sunday night","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"but such blazes are particularly fast-spreading","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"because of a combination of 60mph 96km/h ) winds , low humidity and hot , dry weather .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Ken Moholt-Siebert , a vineyard owner","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"who thought","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"his property had probably been destroyed","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"after he and his family escaped on Sunday night ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"described the suddenness of the disaster .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"`` There was no wind ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"then there would be a rush of wind","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and it would stop .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Then there would be another gust from a different direction .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"The flames wrapped around us , ''","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"he told the LA Times .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"The fires come in a year of record-setting heat and persistent drought ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"according to the San Francisco Chronicle .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"The combination of conditions is more typical of southern California ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"the LA Times reports .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"`` This is exactly what you would expect in the Southern California fall fire season , ''","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Cal Fire director Ken Pimlott said .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Valerie Schropp , a resident of Santa Rosa ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"which was badly affected by the fire ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"told the BBC","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"they had never seen anything like this before .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"`` We do n't expect fires to come into the city","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"and burn at the rate","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"they did , ''","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"Please include a contact number","depth":3},{"id":89,"text":"if you are willing to speak to a BBC journalist .","depth":3},{"id":90,"text":"You can also contact us in the following ways :","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":181,"left":178,"right":180,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":150,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":106,"right":149,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":98,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":92,"right":97,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":94,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":2,"right":93,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":5,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":99,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":101,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":12,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left"